<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000183> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "environs"@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000183> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "b environs c =Def c occurs in b"@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000183> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Mouth environs process of mastication; city environs traffic"@en .
