<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000304> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "c is_manufactured_by o means that there was a process p in which c was built in which a person, or set of people or machines did the work(bore the \"Manufacturer Role\", and those people/and or machines were members or of directed by the organization to do this."@en .
