<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000312> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/COB_0000035> .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000312> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "A relation between a completely executed planned process and a continuant participating in that process. The presence of the continuant at the end of the process is explicitly specified in the objective specification which the process realizes the concretization of."@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000312> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "is specified output of"@en .
