<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0000056> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000112> "this blood clot participates in this blood coagulation"@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0000056> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000112> "this input material (or this output material) participates in this process"@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0000056> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000112> "this investigator participates in this investigation"@en .
