<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0000087> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "a relation between an independent continuant (the bearer) and a role, in which the role specifically depends on the bearer for its existence"@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0000087> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> "A bearer can have many roles, and its roles can exist for different periods of time, but none of its roles can exist when the bearer does not exist. A role need not be realized at all the times that the role exists."@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0000087> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has role"@en .
