<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0025998> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "has relational quality"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0025998> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "a relation between an independent continuant (the bearer) and a relational quality, in which the quality specifically depends on the bearer for its existence"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0025998> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "material has relational quality mass proportion m, and portion of iron has the same relational quality mass proportion m"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0025999
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0025999> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
