<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_17051> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_23367> .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_17051> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "fluoride" .
