<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_18248> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_33521> .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_18248> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "An iron group element atom that has atomic number 26." .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_18248> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "iron atom" .
