<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_18291> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_33521> .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_18291> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "manganese atom" .
