<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_60003> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_60003> .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_60003> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Pure water, a portion of iron atoms. In contrast, salt water 'has part' a portion of pure water and a portion of pure NaCl. Steel 'has part' a 'portion of pure iron', a 'portion of pure carbon' and possibly portions of other alloying- and impurity-elements."@en .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_60003> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000060> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
