_:genid193 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
_:genid193 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#intersectionOf> _:genid196 .
_:genid196 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest> _:genid194 .
_:genid194 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#nil> .
_:genid194 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#first> _:genid195 .
_:genid195 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#someValuesFrom> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000015> .
_:genid195 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#onProperty> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0000056> .
_:genid195 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Restriction> .
_:genid194 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#List> .
