<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000537> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "brinell hardness"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000537> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "An indentation hardness scalar representing a measure of material hardness obtained by indenting the material with a steel or tungsten carbide ball under a specific load."@en .
