<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000577> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "An object aggregate that consists of two or more bonded materials with dissimilar physical or chemical properties which are used to complement each other where the parts remain seperate and distinct in the resulting object aggregate."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000577> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "carbon fibre reinforced polymer\nlaminated glass\nwood\nhard metal composites for abrasive tools" .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000577> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000060> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
