<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000629> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000629> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000015> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000629> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "emission of radiation"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000629> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The emission radiation is a process describing the release of energy in the form of electromagnetic waves or particles from a material."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000629> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000060> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
