<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000630> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The emission of wave radioation is an emission of radiation describing the release of energy in the form of waves, such as electromagnetic or acoustic waves, by a material or system."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000630> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000060> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
