<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000654> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A functional material F is an engineered material which has the disposition to be used for an object O (O consists of F) and O's function is other/more than mechanical load carrying."@en .
