<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000661> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "glass"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000661> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A glass is an engineered material present as an amorphous solid typically formed by rapid cooling of a melt."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000661> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000060> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
