<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000663> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "grain"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000663> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A crystal grain is a crystal that is part of a polycrystal."@en .
