<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000665> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000665> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000602> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000665> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Gravimetrischer Analysator"@de .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000665> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "gravimetric analyzer"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000665> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A device used to measure the mass of a sample to determine its composition or concentration."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000665> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Ein Gerät zur Messung der Masse einer Probe zur Bestimmung ihrer Zusammensetzung oder Konzentration."@de .
