_:genid400 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Restriction> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000816> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Laserspektroskopie"@de .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000816> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "laser spectroscopy"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000816> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A spectroscopy process, that uses laser light to probe the properties of materials."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000816> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Ein Spektroskopie Verfahren, das Laserlicht verwendet, um die Eigenschaften von Materialien zu untersuchen."@de .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000816> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Examples are e.g. laser absorption spectroscopy, laser emission spectroscopy, ultra-fast laser spectroscopy."@en .
