# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000817
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000817> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000817> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> _:genid401 .
