<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000834> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000502> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000834> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "map"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000834> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A map is a 2D information content entity describing a representation of spatial data or relationships, often used in material science for visualizing properties or distributions."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000834> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000060> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
