<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000884> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "physical simulation"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000884> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A simulation method specification describing the use of computational or experimental methods to replicate physical behaviors or processes under defined conditions."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000884> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000060> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
