<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000885> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A pole figure is a map depicting a 2D stereographic projection which represents crystallographic orientations of grains in a polycrystalline material in respect to the sample's reference frame."@en .
