<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000886> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000648> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000886> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Poliermaschine"@de .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000886> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "polishing machine"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000886> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A polishing machine is a forming machine that smooths the surface of a material by rubbing it with a tool, abrasive, or chemical."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000886> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Eine Poliermaschine ist eine Formmaschine, die die Oberfläche eines Materials durch Reiben mit einem Werkzeug, Schleifmittel oder Chemikalien glättet."@de .
