# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000898
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000898> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000898> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000847> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000898> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Druckmessfunktion"@de .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000898> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "pressure measuring function"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000898> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A measuring function performed to determine the pressure of gases or liquids."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000898> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Eine Messfunktion, um den Druck von Gasen oder Flüssigkeiten zu bestimmen."@de .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000898> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000060> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
