# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000902
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000902> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000902> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000899> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000902> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Urformen Aus Dem Spanförmigen Oder Faserförmigen Zustand"@de .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000902> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "primary shaping from the chip or fiber state"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000902> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A primary shaping process that involves forming materials from a chip or fiber state."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000902> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Ein Urformprozess, der das Formen von Materialien aus einem span- oder faserförmigen Zustand beinhaltet."@de .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000902> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Compression molding of wood chips into particle boards."@en .
