<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000928> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "shear testing machine"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000928> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A device used to measure the shear strength of materials by applying a shearing force and measuring deformation."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000928> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Ein Gerät zur Messung der Scherfestigkeit von Materialien durch Anwendung einer Schubkraft und Messung der Verformung."@de .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000929
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000929> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
