<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000936> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A moving device that is guided by a part along its path, providing the mount for objects."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000936> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Eine bewegliche Vorrichtung (Gerät), die von einem Teil entlang ihrer Bahn geführt wird und die Halterung für Objekte bildet."@de .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000937
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000937> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000937> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000602> .
