<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000961> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The sublimation point is a state of matter boundary realized by transition from the solid state to the gaseous state (or vice versa)."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000961> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000060> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
