<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000977> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> "No official definition in DIN"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000977> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Textiles Fügen"@de .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000977> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "textile joining"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000977> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A joining process that involves connecting textile materials."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000977> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Ein Füge Prozess, bei dem textile Materialien miteinander verbunden werden."@de .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000977> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Sewing, Stapling"@en .
