<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000978> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The thermal conductivity is a thermal property describing the ability of a material to conduct heat."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000978> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000060> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
