# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000981
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000981> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000981> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000005> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000981> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> _:genid514 .
_:genid514 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#someValuesFrom> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000520> .
_:genid514 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#onProperty> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000054> .
_:genid514 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Restriction> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000981> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "thermal property"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000981> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A thermal property is a material property representing attributes of a material that describe its behavior under temperature changes, such as thermal conductivity and expansion."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000981> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000060> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
