<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001008> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "process of taking up elctromagnetic radiation by a material entity"@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001009
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001009> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001009> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000602> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001009> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Verschleißprüfmaschine"@de .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001009> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "wear testing machine"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001009> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A device used to test the wear resistance of materials by subjecting them to abrasive conditions."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001009> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Ein Gerät zur Prüfung der Verschleißfestigkeit von Materialien durch Aussetzen dieser Bedingungen unter Abrasivbedingungen."@de .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001010
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001010> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001010> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000849> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001010> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Verschleißprüfverfahren"@de .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001010> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "wear testing process"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001010> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A mechanical property analyzing process that evaluates the resistance of a material to wear and abrasion, simulating real-life conditions of friction."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001010> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Ein Mechanische Eigenschaften Analyseverfahrenn, das den Widerstand eines Materials gegen Verschleiß und Abrieb bewertet und reale Reibungsbedingungen simuliert."@de .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001010> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Wear testing of automotive brake pads to ensure longevity and performance under repetitive braking conditions."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001011
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001011> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001011> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000602> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001011> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Schweißgerät"@de .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001011> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "welding device"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001011> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A device used for joining materials by melting them together, typically with the addition of a filler material."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001011> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Ein Gerät zum Verbinden von Materialien durch Schmelzen, üblicherweise unter Zugabe eines Füllmaterials."@de .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001013
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001013> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001013> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000812> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001013> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Schweißfunktion"@de .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001013> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "welding function"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001013> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A welding function is a joining function that is realized in fusing materials by welding."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001013> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Eine Unterfunktion des Verbindens, die durchgeführt wird, um Materialien durch Schweißtechniken zu verbinden."@de .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001013> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000060> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001014
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001014> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001014> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000957> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001014> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Röntgen Analyseverfahren"@de .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001014> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "x-ray analyzing process"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001014> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A structural property analyzing process that uses X-rays to investigate the internal structure, composition, and properties of materials by measuring the interaction of X-rays with the sample."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001014> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Ein Struktur Eigenschaften Analyseverfahren, das Röntgenstrahlen verwendet, um die innere Struktur, Zusammensetzung und Eigenschaften von Materialien zu untersuchen, indem die Wechselwirkung der Röntgenstrahlen mit der Probe gemessen wird."@de .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001015
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001015> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001015> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001014> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001015> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> _:genid520 .
