<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020000> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A thermodynamic phase is a material entity that forms a homogeneous portion of matter within a thermodynamic system and is characterized by uniform thermodynamic properties."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020000> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000060> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
