_:genid605 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#someValuesFrom> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0025001> .
_:genid605 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#onProperty> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000136> .
