<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020022> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "corrosion"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020022> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "corrosion is a slow chemical or electrochemical degradation process of a material entity due to its interaction with the surrounding environment."@en .
