<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020025> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "obstacle role"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020025> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "An obstacle role is a role of an independent continuant C that is realized in a motion process and indictes that C hinders the motion of a participant in the process."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020025> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "A precipitate or grain boundary may hinder the motion of a dislocation."@en .
