<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020101> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "fraction"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020101> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A proportion is a relational quality between two entities (the whole and the part) which quantifies the relation between the whole and its part."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020101> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000060> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
