<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020102> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020101> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020102> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "mass proportion"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020102> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Mass proportion is a proportion which quantifies the mass of the part relative to the mass of the whole."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020102> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000060> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
