_:genid936 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#onProperty> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000051> .
_:genid936 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Restriction> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020153> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> _:genid937 .
_:genid937 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#someValuesFrom> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000833> .
_:genid937 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#onProperty> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000312> .
