<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020173> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A billet is a relatively compact object that may bear a semi finished product role. At the same time it is a material."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020174
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020174> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
