<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020180> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A tube is a long object with a hollow section and moderate wall thickness that may bear a semi finished product role. At the same time it may be a material."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020181
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020181> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020181> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000030> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020181> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "pipe"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020181> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A tube is a long object with a hollow section and pronounced wall thickness that may bear a semi finished product role. At the same time it may be a material."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020182
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020182> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
