<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020184> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "rolling mill"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020184> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A rolling mill is a device that has part some rolling stand and whose specified input participates in some forming process."@en .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020185
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020185> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
