<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0025997> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Fraction value specification is a value specification that contains information about quantitative share of a part relative to a specified whole."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0025997> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "2.05 wt.% of carbon in steel, 4 vol.% of nitric acid in a solution"@en .
