<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0090000> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "semiconductor"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0090000> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A semiconductor is an engineered material representing a class of materials characterized by an electrical conductivity between that of a conductor and an insulator. This is a result of a range of inexistent energy states in ther electron configuration between the valence and conduction band (bandgap)."@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0090000> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000060> "true"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean> .
