<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0090018> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "bio-based composite"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0090018> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "biocomposite; bio-composite" .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0090018> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "composite consisting of at least one constituent derived from biological or bio-based sources"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0090018> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "such as Wood-Plastic Composite (WPC), Hemp-fiber reinforced Polypropylene" .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0090018> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001032> "https://github.com/materialdigital/core-ontology/issues/354" .
