<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0090019> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0090016> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0090019> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "bio-based chemical"@en .
