<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0090019> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "bio-based material used in chemical reactions as a reactant"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0090019> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "such as bio-based adhesives (e.g. Lignin-based); Bio-epoxy resin." .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0090019> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001032> "https://github.com/materialdigital/core-ontology/issues/354" .
