<https://w3id.org/pmd/log/LOG_0000001> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000412> "https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/supplychain/SupplyChain/IndustrialInventoryRole" .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/log/LOG_0000001> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "industrial inventory role"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/log/LOG_0000001> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "role held by some material entity when it is stored by a bussiness organization and it is intended to be supplied to a customer or to be used or consumed in some product production process"@en-us .
# 
# https://w3id.org/pmd/log/LOG_0000002
<https://w3id.org/pmd/log/LOG_0000002> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/log/LOG_0000002> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://w3id.org/pmd/log/LOG_1000130> .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/log/LOG_0000002> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "business process that results in placing a material entity in the possession of some agent without changing the ownership until the material entity is sold" .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/log/LOG_0000002> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000412> "https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/supplychain/SupplyChain/ConsigningProcess" .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/log/LOG_0000002> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "consigning process"@en .
