<https://w3id.org/pmd/log/LOG_1000140> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "material location change process"@en .
<https://w3id.org/pmd/log/LOG_1000140> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "planned process that results in a material entity moving from one physical location to another"@en-us .
